! Inline formatting

''bold'' text, //italic// text, __underline__ text, ~~strikethrough~~ text.

Super^^script^^ and sub,,script,, and ``inline code`` and @@highlighted@@.

@@.tc-big-green-button a styled span with a class@@
@@color:red;background:yellow;an inline CSS styled span@@

Dashes: an en-dash -- and an em-dash --- in text.

HTML entities: &amp; &copy; &mdash; &#x2192; &nbsp;.

Escaped characters: \/\/ not italic, \'' not bold, literal backtick \`.

A mix on one line: ''bold //and italic// together'' with ``code`` and a
[[WikiLink]] plus a <<currentTiddler>> variable reference.
